<sect1 id="optimizer_page_1optimizer_intro">
<title>Introduction</title>
<para>The <ref refid="classoptimizer" kindref="compound">optimizer</ref> class manages the training loop for machine learning models, including forward/backward passes, gradient updates, and checkpoint management.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="optimizer_page_1optimizer_workflow">
<title>Training Workflow</title>
<para>The optimizer executes the following workflow per epoch:</para>
<para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para><bold>Training Loop</bold>: Forward pass → Loss → Backward pass → Update</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Validation Loop</bold>: Forward pass → Metrics (no gradients)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Checkpoint</bold>: Save model state if improved</para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
